1
00:00:00,470 --> 00:00:02,530
Previously on Fairy Tail:

2
00:00:02,530 --> 00:00:03,440
Aye, sir!

3
00:00:03,440 --> 00:00:06,180
We came to my homeland, Edolas!

4
00:00:06,440 --> 00:00:09,580
It's totally different than Earthland, 
the world we come from...

5
00:00:09,580 --> 00:00:12,740
In this world, cats have a 
higher status than humans!

6
00:00:12,740 --> 00:00:15,330
Which means I'm more 
important than you, Natsu!

7
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:17,660
Uh, can we get back to the main gist, Happy?

8
00:00:17,660 --> 00:00:19,540
That's Happy-<i>senpai</i> to you, bub.

9
00:01:53,870 --> 00:01:55,460
W-What?

10
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:58,930
There's another...

11
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:02,430
...Erza-san?

12
00:02:05,370 --> 00:02:06,500
Erza!

13
00:02:07,510 --> 00:02:08,520
Gray!

14
00:02:09,940 --> 00:02:12,120
Is that Gray Soluge?

15
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:14,320
No... It's the Earthland one!

16
00:02:15,720 --> 00:02:17,860
Where are our friends?

17
00:02:18,820 --> 00:02:22,620
Where are the others you 
turned into a lacrima, huh?!

18
00:02:34,040 --> 00:02:36,060
Erza vs. Erza!

19
00:02:43,920 --> 00:02:45,830
Erza vs. Erza?!

20
00:02:45,830 --> 00:02:49,590
You bastard! You aren't 
going to get away with this!

21
00:02:49,590 --> 00:02:51,820
I'm gonna whup you good!

22
00:02:51,820 --> 00:02:52,910
That's Natsu's voice!

23
00:02:52,910 --> 00:02:53,940
He's near here?

24
00:02:53,940 --> 00:02:55,760
I bet he's up ahead!

25
00:02:55,760 --> 00:02:57,410
Wendy should be with him!

26
00:02:57,640 --> 00:02:59,410
Gray, go on ahead!

27
00:02:59,410 --> 00:03:00,340
Right!

28
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:03,690
Can you stand, Lucy?

29
00:03:03,690 --> 00:03:04,450
Yeah.

30
00:03:08,330 --> 00:03:09,760
How did you get here?

31
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:11,640
I'll fill you in later.

32
00:03:11,640 --> 00:03:12,590
Let's go!

33
00:03:19,980 --> 00:03:22,810
I would have never guessed it 
would be me who stands in my way.

34
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:25,520
This is an odd feeling.

35
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:31,520
I am the Captain of the Second Magic 
Regiment of the Edolas Royal Army, Erza Knightwalker.

36
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:33,970
I am Erza Scarlet.

37
00:03:33,970 --> 00:03:35,940
A Fairy Tail Wizard.

38
00:03:36,730 --> 00:03:41,280
Show me just what the Earthland me has got...

39
00:03:43,070 --> 00:03:44,450
Sylpharion!

40
00:03:47,030 --> 00:03:47,870
She's fast!

41
00:03:49,640 --> 00:03:51,870
In that case, Soaring Armor!

42
00:03:58,300 --> 00:04:01,260
When she changed her armor, 
her speed increased?

43
00:04:05,510 --> 00:04:07,230
Mel Force!

44
00:04:15,270 --> 00:04:16,600
Requip?

45
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:19,650
No... She's changing the shape of her weapon?

46
00:04:19,650 --> 00:04:22,070
Explosion!

47
00:04:29,910 --> 00:04:32,580
The form of her armor has changed again...

48
00:04:32,580 --> 00:04:36,220
Your magic allows you to change the 
shape of your weapons and armor both?

49
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:41,130
It looks like the Edolas me 
can only change her weapons.

50
00:04:41,740 --> 00:04:47,010
Depending on the form of my lance, my 
physical battle abilities can be raised.

51
00:04:47,010 --> 00:04:51,770
The fundamentals are different, but the 
end effect is the same as my The Knight.

52
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:56,520
You'll soon see the true power of 
my magic lance, Ten Commandments!

53
00:04:58,550 --> 00:04:59,480
Come!

54
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:02,070
The lacrima in an open square?

55
00:05:02,300 --> 00:05:03,690
Yeah, that's right.

56
00:05:03,940 --> 00:05:06,780
Seems like that part was 
basically Erza and I.

57
00:05:06,780 --> 00:05:08,020
No way!

58
00:05:08,020 --> 00:05:10,330
But, how did you turn back to normal?

59
00:05:11,250 --> 00:05:12,790
Gajeel showed up.

60
00:05:14,790 --> 00:05:18,110
Alright! I can really go crazy now!

61
00:05:18,870 --> 00:05:21,090
Hey, what are you doing? Stand back!

62
00:05:24,820 --> 00:05:27,630
That Mystogan guy's a shady character,

63
00:05:27,630 --> 00:05:30,220
but I'll believe 'im just 
for a bit this time!

64
00:05:30,970 --> 00:05:32,690
Pole of the Iron Dragon!

65
00:05:32,690 --> 00:05:35,240
Sword of the Iron Dragon!

66
00:05:35,940 --> 00:05:37,940
There's more where that came from!

67
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:52,940
What's this?

68
00:06:04,960 --> 00:06:08,840
What the... Only two?

69
00:06:09,760 --> 00:06:12,260
Hey, wake up! Pay attention!

70
00:06:32,780 --> 00:06:35,070
Ah, you're awake.

71
00:06:35,070 --> 00:06:36,150
Gajeel?

72
00:06:37,210 --> 00:06:38,220
What happened?

73
00:06:38,620 --> 00:06:39,990
I'll explain later.

74
00:06:39,990 --> 00:06:41,040
We're beatin' it outta here!

75
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:42,750
You fiend!

76
00:06:42,750 --> 00:06:44,920
What have you done? You won't get away!

77
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:52,050
I can't use magic!

78
00:06:52,050 --> 00:06:52,840
What?

79
00:06:52,840 --> 00:06:55,470
I said, I'll explain later.

80
00:06:55,470 --> 00:06:58,810
Roar of the Fire Dragon!

81
00:07:09,280 --> 00:07:11,650
Why is it you can use magic?

82
00:07:12,410 --> 00:07:14,280
First, take one of these.

83
00:07:14,280 --> 00:07:15,570
What?

84
00:07:15,570 --> 00:07:16,580
What happened?

85
00:07:16,830 --> 00:07:18,230
Tell us the details!

86
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:21,610
The two of you were turned into a lacrima.

87
00:07:21,610 --> 00:07:22,830
Oh, you're here.

88
00:07:24,370 --> 00:07:26,510
As expected from my Earthland self.

89
00:07:27,090 --> 00:07:29,050
You rescued them splendidly!

90
00:07:29,050 --> 00:07:30,170
There are two...

91
00:07:30,170 --> 00:07:31,550
...Gajeels?!

92
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:36,840
I am the Gajeel from this world.

93
00:07:36,840 --> 00:07:38,770
He's a pretty useful guy.

94
00:07:39,260 --> 00:07:42,140
Look at his face! That's a face 
that says "I get things done."

95
00:07:43,350 --> 00:07:47,170
That aside, what do you mean 
we were turned into lacrima?

96
00:07:47,400 --> 00:07:49,720
That aside...?

97
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:52,870
It means she doesn't give 
a crap about your face.

98
00:07:55,370 --> 00:07:59,700
All the wizards of Fairy Tail 
have been turned into lacrima.

99
00:08:00,380 --> 00:08:03,000
They were after your magic power.

100
00:08:03,280 --> 00:08:06,720
I thought the lacrima in the 
open square was it, but...

101
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:10,510
Even though it was so 
big, it was only you two.

102
00:08:10,510 --> 00:08:12,780
How hella big is the real one?

103
00:08:13,150 --> 00:08:16,260
There was a cut face on that lacrima, yes...

104
00:08:16,260 --> 00:08:20,870
Now that I think about it, that means 
it was a section that was cut off.

105
00:08:20,870 --> 00:08:25,560
There's still so much I want to ask, 
but what were those strange pills?

106
00:08:26,170 --> 00:08:27,900
They're called exballs,

107
00:08:27,900 --> 00:08:31,070
and they're said to be a medicine that 
lets you use magic in this world.

108
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:35,210
We'll talk about the rest 
after you take these.

109
00:08:35,210 --> 00:08:36,860
"Said to be?"

110
00:08:37,980 --> 00:08:40,160
I got 'em from Mystogan.

111
00:08:40,160 --> 00:08:41,680
From Mystogan?

112
00:08:44,450 --> 00:08:47,730
I see! Gajeel is also a Dragon Slayer,

113
00:08:47,730 --> 00:08:50,590
so Anima didn't work on him either, 
just like Natsu and Wendy!

114
00:08:50,590 --> 00:08:54,520
He wasn't sucked over here, 
but remained in Earthland?

115
00:08:54,520 --> 00:08:57,630
Then, Mystogan sent Gajeel here.

116
00:08:57,630 --> 00:09:01,100
Why won't he come here himself?

117
00:09:01,370 --> 00:09:06,410
In this world Dragon Slayer Magic 
can be used for a bunch of things.

118
00:09:06,410 --> 00:09:10,010
It can turn our friends turned 
into lacrima back to normal!

119
00:09:10,290 --> 00:09:11,630
Really?

120
00:09:11,630 --> 00:09:14,860
We know where that lacrima is!

121
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:16,560
Really, Happy?

122
00:09:16,560 --> 00:09:17,490
Aye!

123
00:09:17,770 --> 00:09:22,410
Gajeel's running wild in the city right 
now searching for that giant lacrima!

124
00:09:25,290 --> 00:09:28,260
Can you take Gajeel to where the lacrima is?

125
00:09:28,260 --> 00:09:31,590
Gajeel should be able to turn 
everyone back to normal, right?

126
00:09:31,590 --> 00:09:37,260
To be precise, Natsu and Wendy should also 
be able to, but they wouldn't know how.

127
00:09:38,050 --> 00:09:41,810
Got it! I'll take Gajeel there!

128
00:09:41,810 --> 00:09:44,670
Wait... Are you gonna be okay, Happy?

129
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,520
He will be fine.

130
00:09:48,520 --> 00:09:51,510
We've got to go find Natsu and Wendy, too!

131
00:09:51,510 --> 00:09:52,070
Yeah!

132
00:09:59,860 --> 00:10:01,700
Look, there's a door!

133
00:10:01,700 --> 00:10:03,930
The two of them are in there!

134
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:09,160
Natsu!

135
00:10:09,160 --> 00:10:10,120
Wendy!

136
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:12,740
You okay? Hang in there!

137
00:10:12,740 --> 00:10:13,880
Wendy!

138
00:10:14,460 --> 00:10:16,510
Natsu, wake up!

139
00:10:16,510 --> 00:10:18,510
Natsu is unconscious?

140
00:10:18,750 --> 00:10:20,130
So is Wendy!

141
00:10:20,130 --> 00:10:24,270
I'm sorry! I'm sorry, Wendy!

142
00:10:25,520 --> 00:10:28,520
Hey, Natsu! How long are you gonna sleep?

143
00:10:28,520 --> 00:10:30,520
Wake up already, you bum!

144
00:10:30,520 --> 00:10:32,270
Hey, Gray...

145
00:10:33,490 --> 00:10:36,000
Anyway, we'll get them to take exballs.

146
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:37,990
Open your damn mouth, Natsu!

147
00:10:37,990 --> 00:10:39,240
Those are...

148
00:10:39,700 --> 00:10:44,950
We got them from Gajeel... Didn't 
you get one from Mystogan?

149
00:10:47,620 --> 00:10:48,910
Eat this.

150
00:10:49,670 --> 00:10:50,820
What's that?

151
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:55,270
Now that you mention it, maybe 
I do remember him making me...

152
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:58,910
It's a medicine that lets 
you use magic in this world!

153
00:10:58,910 --> 00:11:00,220
It is?

154
00:11:06,460 --> 00:11:07,530
Natsu!

155
00:11:09,930 --> 00:11:12,010
Good. Next up is Wendy!

156
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:16,340
Are you okay, Natsu?

157
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:23,340
G-Gotta stop them, or...

158
00:11:24,660 --> 00:11:26,010
Stop...?

159
00:11:33,350 --> 00:11:34,170
Natsu!

160
00:11:35,060 --> 00:11:36,510
Hey, you!

161
00:11:39,520 --> 00:11:40,790
Wendy!

162
00:11:41,240 --> 00:11:42,300
Wendy!

163
00:11:42,300 --> 00:11:43,220
Are you okay?

164
00:11:45,530 --> 00:11:47,720
Carla... Everyone...

165
00:11:47,980 --> 00:11:49,310
Hang in there!

166
00:11:50,540 --> 00:11:55,020
We're in trouble... Everyone 
in the guild will be...

167
00:12:03,560 --> 00:12:06,120
Sorry to keep you waiting, Your Highness.

168
00:12:07,180 --> 00:12:10,300
The extraction is complete, for now.

169
00:12:10,830 --> 00:12:12,750
Excellent work.

170
00:12:12,750 --> 00:12:16,750
The magic power of dragons 
is indeed magnificent.

171
00:12:17,570 --> 00:12:22,010
With this, it will be a trivial matter 
to convert <i>that</i> into a weapon...

172
00:12:29,260 --> 00:12:37,100
In order to destroy Extalia, the Royal Army 
intends to crash the giant lacrima into it!

173
00:12:38,380 --> 00:12:43,650
They're going to use everyone 
at Fairy Tail as a giant bomb!

174
00:12:44,600 --> 00:12:47,570
I have been waiting for this time!

175
00:12:48,180 --> 00:12:53,160
The magic power of the Exceeds and 
the lacrima will explode, and fuse...

176
00:12:53,160 --> 00:12:58,640
And magic power will rain down 
for eternity on our kingdom!

177
00:13:14,240 --> 00:13:18,130
In Edolas, they have floating islands.

178
00:13:18,130 --> 00:13:20,280
I'm sure you all saw some of them, right?

179
00:13:20,280 --> 00:13:23,230
It seems like they float 
using Extalia's magic power.

180
00:13:24,110 --> 00:13:28,360
It said in the book that they control 
the balance of magic in this world.

181
00:13:28,360 --> 00:13:31,850
And our friends that have been turned 
into a lacrima are on one of the islands?

182
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:34,750
One right next to Extalia, yes...

183
00:13:39,050 --> 00:13:45,380
Right now, floating above the Royal City 
where we are, is Extalia and the lacrima.

184
00:13:47,130 --> 00:13:51,680
They'll hit the floating island with 
Dragon Slayer Magic to accelerate it,

185
00:13:52,230 --> 00:13:56,350
and crash it into Extalia. That's 
what the Royal Army is planning.

186
00:13:58,410 --> 00:13:59,850
What'll happen?

187
00:14:00,250 --> 00:14:06,530
The magic power of Extalia and Fairy 
Tail will collide, explode, and fuse...

188
00:14:06,980 --> 00:14:10,470
They said magic power will rain down 
on this country for eternity...

189
00:14:11,190 --> 00:14:13,930
If they do that, then everyone 
from the guild will be...

190
00:14:13,930 --> 00:14:15,150
They'll disappear!

191
00:14:17,810 --> 00:14:19,200
Someone's coming, damn it!

192
00:14:19,430 --> 00:14:20,370
An enemy?

193
00:14:21,710 --> 00:14:22,880
Here they come!

194
00:14:26,530 --> 00:14:28,300
What's with you?!

195
00:14:28,300 --> 00:14:29,970
There were two Erzas!

196
00:14:29,970 --> 00:14:32,610
What the... How the... Why?!

197
00:14:34,340 --> 00:14:36,350
Battles of the giant monsters?!

198
00:14:36,350 --> 00:14:39,180
Is it the end of this world?!

199
00:14:43,400 --> 00:14:45,420
Oh, it's Gray!

200
00:14:45,420 --> 00:14:49,810
You won't shut up. You won't calm 
down... Man, you're annoying.

201
00:14:49,810 --> 00:14:53,410
This is the Gray we know, from Earthland.

202
00:14:53,410 --> 00:14:54,120
What?!

203
00:14:54,120 --> 00:14:58,210
A lot of stuff happened and we're 
here now. So are Gajeel and Erza.

204
00:14:58,210 --> 00:15:00,540
Happy went to stop the lacrima.

205
00:15:00,790 --> 00:15:02,570
Oh, you're right!

206
00:15:02,570 --> 00:15:04,080
Gray-san is here!

207
00:15:07,180 --> 00:15:08,850
What, you just noticed now?

208
00:15:08,850 --> 00:15:09,720
Yeah.

209
00:15:11,640 --> 00:15:15,590
Well, we're in a basement, so there's 
no sunlight on me, I suppose.

210
00:15:15,590 --> 00:15:18,700
I can barely see myself!

211
00:15:18,700 --> 00:15:20,180
Hit a sore spot...

212
00:15:20,180 --> 00:15:23,850
Wait, did you guys come here to save me?

213
00:15:23,850 --> 00:15:25,920
You're safe too, Lucy?

214
00:15:25,920 --> 00:15:28,710
You just noticed me now?

215
00:15:28,710 --> 00:15:32,700
Stupid me... I should have 
said that first thing!

216
00:15:32,700 --> 00:15:34,710
Thank you very much!

217
00:15:35,190 --> 00:15:36,340
No biggie.

218
00:15:38,550 --> 00:15:42,450
I knew you all would come and save us, Carla!

219
00:15:43,180 --> 00:15:44,340
Thank you!

220
00:15:49,200 --> 00:15:52,210
Not that I care, but put 
on some clothes, Gray!

221
00:15:52,210 --> 00:15:54,420
Oh! Since when have I...

222
00:15:54,420 --> 00:15:56,200
Since the beginning.

223
00:16:00,370 --> 00:16:02,480
'Kay, all set!

224
00:16:03,560 --> 00:16:06,860
We'll find the king, and stop 
them from ramming the lacrima!

225
00:16:06,860 --> 00:16:07,570
Yeah!

226
00:16:08,400 --> 00:16:11,530
Wait! There are two giant monsters out there!

227
00:16:11,530 --> 00:16:12,590
This way!

228
00:16:12,590 --> 00:16:14,570
You sure it's okay to leave Erza on her own?

229
00:16:15,210 --> 00:16:16,830
This is Erza we're talking about.

230
00:16:16,830 --> 00:16:18,330
But then again, so is her opponent.

231
00:16:19,120 --> 00:16:22,760
Carla, we'll head to Extalia.

232
00:16:23,450 --> 00:16:25,050
W-Why?

233
00:16:25,050 --> 00:16:28,840
We have to tell them to take shelter 
because the kingdom is going to attack!

234
00:16:28,840 --> 00:16:32,260
But we're going to stop that attack, right?

235
00:16:32,260 --> 00:16:35,050
Of course we'll stop it. We'll never 
let them do it, no matter what!

236
00:16:35,050 --> 00:16:37,680
That's because I believe in 
Natsu-san and the others.

237
00:16:37,680 --> 00:16:42,350
But we don't know what other kinds 
of weapons the Royal Army has!

238
00:16:42,350 --> 00:16:45,710
We have to warn them of 
the danger, just in case.

239
00:16:45,710 --> 00:16:47,980
Because that's something we can do!

240
00:16:48,220 --> 00:16:50,370
No! I don't want to go back!

241
00:16:50,370 --> 00:16:53,590
I don't care what happens to the Exceeds...

242
00:16:57,170 --> 00:17:00,330
It's not about being human, 
or being an Exceed...

243
00:17:14,290 --> 00:17:18,500
As fellow living things, 
there is something we can do.

244
00:17:24,470 --> 00:17:26,330
The Exceeds are just...

245
00:17:37,900 --> 00:17:42,040
I'll always be by your side. 
You don't have to be afraid.

246
00:17:42,320 --> 00:17:43,170
Okay?

247
00:17:49,060 --> 00:17:50,670
I understand.

248
00:17:55,170 --> 00:17:57,420
Gajeel!

249
00:17:58,490 --> 00:18:00,790
Cat! You're okay?

250
00:18:00,790 --> 00:18:04,890
I'll lead you to where the lacrima is 
that all our friends were turned into!

251
00:18:05,780 --> 00:18:08,390
Hey, wait... Don't just grab me!

252
00:18:08,810 --> 00:18:11,650
How do you return the people 
to normal from a lacrima?

253
00:18:13,110 --> 00:18:15,640
You shatter it with Dragon Slayer Magic!

254
00:18:16,390 --> 00:18:18,710
That actually works?

255
00:18:18,710 --> 00:18:22,650
I did exactly like Mystogan 
said, so no complainin'!

256
00:18:22,650 --> 00:18:25,110
By the way, Mystogan didn't come?

257
00:18:25,110 --> 00:18:26,500
How should I know?

258
00:18:33,650 --> 00:18:35,160
I-It's big.

259
00:18:35,160 --> 00:18:37,670
It's bigger than I anticipated.

260
00:18:37,670 --> 00:18:40,950
Man, this guild's a real pain in the ass!

261
00:18:43,140 --> 00:18:45,680
When I get home, I'm gonna 
eat my fill of iron!

262
00:18:45,680 --> 00:18:47,650
You can do it, Gajeel!

263
00:18:52,560 --> 00:18:54,410
Who the hell are you?!

264
00:18:59,730 --> 00:19:01,010
That guy's...

265
00:19:04,910 --> 00:19:09,050
Captain of the First Magic 
Regiment of the Royal Army...

266
00:19:10,370 --> 00:19:12,130
Panther Lily.

267
00:19:13,080 --> 00:19:17,560
This lacrima is completely 
crucial for this operation.

268
00:19:18,510 --> 00:19:20,210
I will not let you!

269
00:19:20,840 --> 00:19:23,850
Wings? Don't tell me he's an Exceed?!

270
00:19:23,850 --> 00:19:25,640
Stand back, Cat.

271
00:19:25,640 --> 00:19:28,140
Sword of the Iron Dragon!

272
00:19:28,650 --> 00:19:31,100
Buster Ma'am!

273
00:19:42,780 --> 00:19:45,870
What the heck is with that 
stupidly giant sword?

274
00:19:50,330 --> 00:19:51,590
This guy...

275
00:19:58,600 --> 00:20:02,090
Can someone like you defeat <i>me</i>?

276
00:20:06,140 --> 00:20:09,030
Where is this King person?

277
00:20:09,030 --> 00:20:11,190
Well, he's the King, right?

278
00:20:11,190 --> 00:20:13,100
I bet he's someplace real important!

279
00:20:13,990 --> 00:20:16,190
And where is a real important place?

280
00:20:16,190 --> 00:20:20,800
How the hell should I know? I just got 
here in the castle, and so did you!

281
00:20:21,210 --> 00:20:22,880
Sheesh...

282
00:20:22,880 --> 00:20:27,740
The cell was in a high place, and the 
middle garden is really complex looking.

283
00:20:28,310 --> 00:20:31,780
It's like a concentric castle city, except 
something is a little different...

284
00:20:32,070 --> 00:20:37,640
Common knowledge on Earthland isn't going to help 
understand Edolas castle construction here at all!

285
00:20:39,030 --> 00:20:41,070
What are you talking about, Lucy?

286
00:20:41,070 --> 00:20:43,680
So you're saying, the 
place's architecture sucks.

287
00:20:43,680 --> 00:20:49,550
Yeah. I wouldn't be surprised if there was 
like, an amusement park in the castle somewhere.

288
00:20:52,140 --> 00:20:54,360
There is!

289
00:20:54,360 --> 00:20:56,120
What?

290
00:21:04,460 --> 00:21:06,820
There really is an amusement park!

291
00:21:07,200 --> 00:21:10,780
Hey... You think the king 
here's right in the head?

292
00:21:12,480 --> 00:21:16,120
Looking at your face, I think 
you'd get along just fine.

293
00:21:27,980 --> 00:21:30,480
How fun...

294
00:21:33,700 --> 00:21:36,610
It really is fun.

295
00:21:46,570 --> 00:21:49,950
This, like, crazy fun magic power...

296
00:21:49,950 --> 00:21:53,240
It's gonna disappear from 
this world soon, whoa...

297
00:21:56,240 --> 00:21:59,210
Don't you people understand how we feel?

298
00:22:00,850 --> 00:22:04,230
We are going to get an infinite 
supply of magic power.

299
00:22:05,430 --> 00:22:08,470
No matter what it takes to get it...

300
00:22:13,940 --> 00:22:16,320
We're desperate here!

301
00:22:17,480 --> 00:22:21,100
We won't let anyone interfere!

302
00:23:56,630 --> 00:23:57,970
What's this?

303
00:23:57,970 --> 00:23:59,910
There's an amusement park inside the castle!

304
00:23:59,910 --> 00:24:01,800
Whoa, awesome!

305
00:24:01,800 --> 00:24:04,230
Does this all move using magic?

306
00:24:04,230 --> 00:24:05,630
Probably.

307
00:24:05,630 --> 00:24:08,070
But who cares about that right now?!

308
00:24:08,070 --> 00:24:10,510
For now, let's just play to 
our heart's content, Happy!

309
00:24:10,510 --> 00:24:13,510
You've completely forgotten 
our goal, Natsu...

310
00:24:13,960 --> 00:24:16,510
Next time: It's Life!!!!

311
00:24:16,510 --> 00:24:19,310
And besides, there's a lot 
of things you ride here.

312
00:24:19,310 --> 00:24:21,310
I-I think I'm gonna hurl...

313
00:24:21,310 --> 00:24:24,570
Please stop getting queasy 
just from your imagination...

314
00:24:24,570 --> 00:24:26,800


